org.jruby.util

Class Dir

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jruby.util.Dir

  • public class Dir
extends Object
    This class exists as a counterpart to the dir.c file in MRI source. It contains many methods useful for File matching and Globbing.
    Author:
    Ola Bini
